<plot>After the death of his mother, a middle-aged man seeks the admiration of his nephew by inviting him to a hotel in a seedy riverbend town. As a way of catharsis, he arranges for a woman to meet his nephew/surrogate son in a selfish act of redemption; as a result Raymond brings larger problems between the two to the surface.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?460934</url></doc>
